INSTALL

very preliminary installation instructions:

1. make symbolic links for the following files:

iVend.pmod -> roxen/server/lib/pike/modules/iVend.pmod
Commerce.pmod -> roxen/server/lib/pike/modules/Commerce.pmod
messages.h -> roxen/server/lib/pike/include/messages.h

2. make sure that the iVend distribution directory is in Roxen's module
search path. 

for more information, see doc/README.

24 march 1998
